Package dev.nokee.ide.xcode

Interface XcodeIdeProjectExtension

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    XcodeIdeWorkspaceExtension
    public interface XcodeIdeProjectExtension
    The configuration for mapping a Gradle project to Xcode projects. The project extension is register to sub-projects where the Xcode IDE plugin is applied. The workspace extension, that is XcodeIdeWorkspaceExtension, is register to the root project instead.
    Since:
    0.3

      • getProductTypes

        XcodeIdeProductTypes getProductTypes()
        Returns a repository containing all the known product types by the plugin. This method is provided as a convenience when configuring the Xcode project via the DSL. It is equivalent to importing the XcodeIdeProductTypes class and accessing the public field: 
         plugins {
     id 'dev.nokee.xcode-ide'
 }

 import dev.nokee.ide.xcode.XcodeIdeProductTypes

 xcode {
     projects.register('foo') {
         targets.register('Foo') {
             productType = XcodeIdeProductTypes.APPLICATION
         }
     }
 }
        Returns:
        a XcodeIdeProductTypes instance to access all known product types via the DSL, never, null.
